- "structural veins" metaphorically refers to the walls;
- "mean length of their walls" is the average length of walls;
- "count of these walls" is the total number of walls;
- "most recent inspection date" is the latest date the walls were inspected;
- "average vertical and horizontal material densities" refer to the vertical and horizontal densities of the wall material.

sql:
SELECT COUNT(wall_id) AS good_wall_count
FROM wall_conditions
WHERE condition = 'good';

SELECT wc.condition, COUNT(wc.wall_condition_id) AS wall_count
FROM wall_conditions wc
GROUP BY wc.condition;
